            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/kkd/about-the-ministry/Organisation/Departments/Cultural-Heritage-Department.html?id=590159" title="">
                    Cultural Heritage Department
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The areas of responsibility for the Cultural Heritage Department include buildings, museums, archives, libraries, language and literature, in addition to coordinating international issues in the field of culture.

            </p>
