            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/kkd/about-the-ministry/Organisation/Departments/Department-for-the-Arts.html?id=590158" title="">
                    Department for the Arts
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The areas of responsibility for the Department for the Arts include music, dramatic art, pictorial art, The National Museum, Arts Council Norway, The Cultural Rucksack and the Cultural Walking Cane, architecture, art in public spaces, design, artists’ policy and cultural diversity.

            </p>
