            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/kkd/about-the-ministry/Organisation/Departments/department-of-information.html?id=1487" title="">
                    Department of Information
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The Department of Information communicate questions from the press to the political leadership and departments. The department helps the press and the public to find the right department for comment, background information and case information. Information Department is responsible for the Ministry's website.
            </p>
