            <h2>
                <a href="/en/dep/kkd/about-the-ministry/Organisation/Departments/Department-of-Media-Policy-and-Copyright-.html?id=1535" title="">
                    Department of Media Policy and Copyright 
                </a>
            </h2>
            <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
            
            <p>
                The department is responsible for national and international media issues, including issues concerning the press, broadcasting and copyright legislation, film and video legislation, film policy etc. Moreover, the department is responsible for the state lotteries run by Norsk Tipping and for regulating gaming and lotteries run by private organisations. The Norwegian Media Authority, the Norwegian Film Institute and The Norwegian Gaming and Foundation Authority are all under the jurisdiction of the department. Furthermore, the department attends to the state’s ownership interests for the Norwegian Broadcasting Corporation, Filmparken and Norsk Tipping. 

            </p>
